{"tid":1620513,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"緊急法一出，個個都緊急咁去花旗開戶，你開咗未?","createTime":"2019-10-04T10:37:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T10:37:40.000Z","uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"66f5dfa355b7f681e4b6ec433a29e5b6d019fec8","tid":1620513,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:37:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/htoRFf5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhtoRFf5.jpg&h=9b937699&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n元朗花旗<br />\n10月4 號<br />\n16:28 嘅相<br />\n<br />\n想講嘅係，777 一推出緊急法，個個都緊急咁去花旗開戶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且大家望下張相，中間坐係度嘅兩位媽咪級姐姐都討論話要開離岸戶口，話怕 777 突然用緊急法「徵用」佢地個戶口啲錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以要來問下資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟住中間位叔叔又插嘴話，777 依家就唔畀蒙面，係借口，下次就係凍結大家啲錢，最大問題係唔使事前通知，啲錢搬得走就搬喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以各位，快啲同屋企人討論下開離岸戶口嘅事，一個人未必夠錢到門檻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但一家人入面搵個人做代表去開，或者夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果未夠離岸戶口門檻都好，去開個美帝嘅花旗戶口係無壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且將啲錢由中資銀行轉哂去花旗亦都係抗爭手段之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}